data.description: Welcome Home to this stunning 4-bed, 3-bath Maston floor plan by KB Home in Bannon Lakes. With over 3,200 square feet, this property offers plenty of room for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll notice the beautiful LVP flooring and the elegant 9' ceilings adorned with crown molding, creating a sense of sophistication throughout. The kitchen boasts a gas range and stainless steel appliances, while the custom shelving in the pantry adds convenience and storage space. The screened lanai, featuring Shark coating, provides a peaceful retreat where you can enjoy the serene views of the pond. The paver patio is perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply relaxing. Additional features include upgraded 15 seer dual-zone HVAC and a 2-car garage with Shark coating and overhead storage.
